Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:44.68,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,そ… そう 言わずに｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:44.96,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,うるせえ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:46.14,Internal Dialogue,,0,0,0,,｢鳴かぬなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.22,Internal Dialogue,,0,0,0,,鳴かせてみせよう
