Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.90,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,織田 信長を支えさせてくれぬか？》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:36.56,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,《まずは
